        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(X(\\Omega)=\\{0,1,2,3\\}\\)</span> et <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(Y(\\Omega)=\\{0,1\\}\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "8fa96693-7781-4cae-afe0-09cca4218719",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Déterminer la loi de $X$ et calculer son espérance.",
        "html": "<p>Déterminer la loi de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X\\)</span> et\ncalculer son espérance.</p>\n"
