        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(X\\sim\n\\mathcal{H}(3,\\frac{5}{9},9)\\)</span> et <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\E(X)=3\\times \\frac{5}{9}=\\frac{5}{3}\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
