        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(Y\\sim\n\\mathcal{H}(3,\\frac{1}{9},9)\\)</span> et <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\E(Y)=3\\times \\frac{1}{9}=\\frac{1}{3}\\)</span></p>\n"
